<br>
I've just been readingsome reviews and that, and there was an article regardin Everquest on the PS2.  The man from Verant sez - <br>
<br>
&quot;I think the PS2 version will end being a bery different game.  There are definitely a lot of questions: how do you patch in? How do you communicate with others without a keyboard.&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Hello!<br>
<br>
